  <div class="faq-list">
    <div class="faq-item fi"><div class="faq-q" onclick="tf(this)">How much do dental implants cost in Islamabad? <span class="faq-arr">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">At FZ International Hospital, dental implants start from Rs. 80,000 per implant. This is highly competitive compared to other clinics in Islamabad which typically charge Rs. 100,000–150,000. Treatment is performed by our UK-trained Oral Surgeon with MJDF and MDS OMFS qualifications. WhatsApp us for an exact quote after assessment.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item fi"><div class="faq-q" onclick="tf(this)">What is the price of braces in Islamabad? <span class="faq-arr">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Metal braces by our FCPS Orthodontist start from Rs. 35,000 — with easy monthly installment plans. Clear/invisible aligners start from Rs. 80,000. Invisible (lingual) braces that go behind your teeth start from Rs. 150,000. Braces consultation is Rs. 1,500. Monthly adjustment visits range from Rs. 3,000–5,000 depending on complexity.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item fi"><div class="faq-q" onclick="tf(this)">Is root canal treatment painful? <span class="faq-arr">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">With modern techniques and proper local anesthesia, root canal treatment is virtually painless. Most patients report feeling pressure but no pain during the procedure. You may feel mild soreness for 1–2 days afterward, easily managed with over-the-counter pain relief. Same-day root canal is available — WhatsApp us for urgent appointments.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item fi"><div class="faq-q" onclick="tf(this)">How long do dental implants last? <span class="faq-arr">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Dental implants are designed to last a lifetime with proper care. The titanium post fuses with your jawbone (osseointegration) and becomes a permanent part of your anatomy. The crown on top typically lasts 15–25 years. With good oral hygiene and regular dental checkups, implants can last 30+ years.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item fi"><div class="faq-q" onclick="tf(this)">How long does braces treatment take? <span class="faq-arr">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Treatment duration depends on the severity of misalignment. Mild cases may take 12 months. Average cases take 18–24 months. Complex bite corrections may take 24–36 months. Our FCPS Orthodontist will give you a precise estimate after clinical examination and X-rays during your Rs. 1,500 consultation.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item fi"><div class="faq-q" onclick="tf(this)">Where is the dental clinic and can I book same-day? <span class="faq-arr">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">We are at 204 Street, Shaheen Commercial, Jinnah Garden, Islamabad — conveniently accessible from DHA, Bahria Town, PWD, Anchorage, Rawalpindi, and all of Islamabad. Same-day appointments are available subject to availability. WhatsApp +92 311 1529680 for fastest booking — we typically reply within minutes.</div></div>
